# Agronomist sign-off ledger for the abatement measure library.
# Append one JSON object per review decision. This is the audit trail that lets a
# measure pass the production reviewed_only gate. It is append-only: to change a
# decision, add a new line (last line per measure_id wins).
#
# Record shape:
#   {"measure_id": "meas.n.split_application.gh", "reviewer": "Dr Ama Owusu",
#    "reviewed_at": "2026-07-20", "decision": "approved",
#    "notes": "Effect magnitude conservative; timing guidance sound for Ghana."}
#
# decision: "approved" | "rejected" | "needs_changes"
# Only "approved" stamps provenance.reviewed_by and flips is_reviewed.
#
# Use  python review.py  to generate the worksheet an agronomist reviews against.
# No measures are approved yet: the whole library is draft until this ledger is filled.
